  "summary": "As of mid-2026, no major financial regulator (US SEC / CFTC / FinCEN, UK FCA, Japan FSA, Singapore MAS, EU ESMA / EBA) has formally granted AI agents independent legal personhood, and no major tax authority (US IRS, UK HMRC, Japan NTA, Singapore IRAS, OECD) has created a new \"AI agent\" tax category.",
